<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.9.6">
<l>maṟukkival valaippaṭuttik kumaittiṭṭuk koṉṟuṇpa</l>
<l>raṟapporuḷai yaṟintōrā rivaiyeṉṉa vulakiyaṟkai</l>
<l>veṟittuḷava muṭiyāṉē viṉaiyēṉai yuṉakkaṭimai</l>
<l>yaṟakkoṇṭā yiṉiyeṉṉā ramutēkū yaruḷāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who perplex, catch in strong nets, tread down, kill [and] eat</l>
<l>fully knowing the meaning they won’t know. What are these? the nature of the world,</l>
<l>o you with a perfumed tulsi crown, you who have fully taken me with [bad] karma</l>
<l>into your servantship. Now, my rare ambrosia, graciously call [me].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
